FuncDef: This command overrides the scheduling rate applied to the HS WRR group in Kb/s. Alternatively, the keywordmaxcan be specified which removes the bandwidth limitation on the HS WRR group. The override rate type must match the corresponding rate type within the applied QoS policy.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the scheduling rate of the HS WRR group in Kb/s. Values-1 to 2000000000, max.
